    "description": "Get into the aerocycle and let's go!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180150/extras/eeced4f38ef1ead067812cb496ed2d99.avif?t=1756316778\" width=620 height=69 /></span><br><strong>ITRP _ Aero Star</strong> offers you to overcome an obstacle course.<br>Push your skills to the limit on an unpredictable track. Each stage is unique. <br>Somewhere you need to demonstrate mastery of reaction. Somewhere spatial thinking. Somewhere discretion.<br>Don't be afraid to make mistakes. Fear what follows. The track is dangerous and treacherous, but fair – any mistakes will be forgiven if you prove your superiority to it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180150/extras/f6755479e9712d667ac18c2ddcae56bf.poster.avif?t=1756316778\" width=620 height=251 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180150/extras/f6755479e9712d667ac18c2ddcae56bf.webm?t=1756316778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>You are a volunteer who has agreed to take part in special research.<br>It is extremely important that the test be as painless as possible, so carefully prepare for the race.<br>You have been provided with everything you need to be fully armed, and your personal supervisor will carefully monitor your development.<br>The test will be completed successfully if you get to the very end of the track, overcoming all its challenges.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Scripted track. Low level of the randomness factor.<br></li><li>Constantly changing mechanics that force you to adapt to new conditions.<br></li><li>All segments are unique and do not repeat throughout the game.<br></li><li>It will take no more than an hour to get from the beginning to the end of the track.<br></li><li>Checkpoints save and update progress.<br></li><li>Progression system based on the reduction of previously received damage.<br></li><li>Several endings, depending on the exact way the track was overcome.<br></li><li>Training mode that allows you to configure the track in detail.<br></li><li>A challenge worthy of a true hardcore racing fan!</li></ul>",
